ter  gamble for us billion press investigators estimate that he stood to gain more than  million personally in the purchase kilts is currently a partner at centerview partners an investment banking and private equity firm based in new york city in that role he was involved in the sale of big heart pet brands and is now looking to raise a special purpose acquisition company spac for a new acquisition he was then elected to the board of directors at the new york times company in  he is a member of the cato institute board of directors kilts is a  graduate of knox college in galesburg illinois and received his master of business administration degree from the university of chicago booth school of business in addition as an undergraduate student at knox college kilts was also a member of the delta chapter of tau kappa epsilon fraternity referencesedit  big heart pet brands is the new name for del monte foods’ pet products business centerview retrieved june     centerview privateequity arm planning to launch blankcheck company wsj retrieved june     board of directors cato institute retrieved  march   external linksedit where gillette ceo went wrong this businessrelated biographical article is a stub you can help wikipedia by expanding it v t e retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitlejamesmkiltsoldid categories university of chicago booth school of business alumniknox college illinois alumnicato institute peoplebusiness biography stubshidden categories all stub articles navigation menu personal tools not logged intalkcontributionscreate accountlog in namespaces article talk variants views read edit view history more search navigation main pagecontentsfeatured contentcurrent eventsrandom articledonate to wikipediawikipedia store interaction helpabout wikipediacommunity portalrecent changescontact page tools what links hererelated changesupload filespecial pagespermanent linkpage informationwikidata itemcite this page printexport create a bookdownload as pdfprintab